            <section id="about" class="gov_content-block">
                <h2 class="gov_content-block__title">
                    <a class="gov_content-block__title-link" href="/about/" data-navigation="about-title">
                        About government
                    </a>
                </h2>

                <div class="gov_sublayout  gov_sublayout--twocols">
                        <div class="gov_homepage-fm">

                            <h3 class="gov_homepage-fm__title">First Minister</h3>

                            <picture class="gov_homepage-fm__image">
                                <source width="360" height="202" srcset="/binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-jpg/humza-new-2024-jpg/govscot%3Asmallcolumns 1x, /binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-jpg/humza-new-2024-jpg/govscot%3Asmallcolumnsdoubled 2x" media="(max-width: 767px)">
                                <source width="352" height="197" srcset="/binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-jpg/humza-new-2024-jpg/govscot%3Amediumsixcolumns 1x, /binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-jpg/humza-new-2024-jpg/govscot%3Amediumsixcolumnsdoubled 2x" media="(max-width: 991px)">
                                <source width="128" height="71" srcset="/binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/govscot%3Alargetwocolumns 1x, /binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/govscot%3Alargetwocolumnsdoubled 2x" media="(max-width: 1199px)">

                                <img alt="Humza Yousaf" loading="lazy" width="160" height="160" src="/binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/govscot%3Axlargetwocolumns" srcset="/binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/govscot%3Axlargetwocolumns 1x, /binaries/content/gallery/navigationcardimages/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/humza-new-2024-square-jpg/govscot%3Axlargetwocolumnsdoubled 2x">
                            </picture>

                            <div class="gov_homepage-fm__content">
                                <p>As head of the Scottish Government, the First Minister is responsible for the overall development, implementation and presentation of the administration's policies and for promoting and representing Scotland at home and overseas.</p>

                                <a class="gov_icon-link  gov_icon-link--major" href="/about/who-runs-government/first-minister/">
                                    <span class="gov_icon-link__text">Read more <span class="visually-hidden">about the First Minister</span></span>
                                    <span class="gov_icon-link__icon  gov_icon-link__icon--chevron" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <h3>How government works</h3>

<p>The Scottish Government is made up of:</p>

<div class="stat-boxes"><a href="/about/who-runs-government/first-minister/" class="stat-box"><span class="stat-box__value">1</span><span class="stat-box__label"><span class="stat-box__label-text">First Minister</span></span></a> <a href="/about/who-runs-government/cabinet-and-ministers/" class="stat-box"><span class="stat-box__value">9</span><span class="stat-box__label"><span class="stat-box__label-text">Cabinet Secretaries</span></span></a> <a href="/about/who-runs-government/cabinet-and-ministers/" class="stat-box"><span class="stat-box__value">16</span><span class="stat-box__label"><span class="stat-box__label-text">Other Ministers</span></span></a></div>                        </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

